2026-05-15T23:28:36.4418250Z 21    <!--
2026-05-15T23:28:36.4418651Z 22        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T23:28:36.4418848Z 23        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T23:28:36.4419218Z 24          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
